\section{Stats Results}
\label{\detokenize{index:stats-results}}
\sphinxAtStartPar
The \sphinxhref{https://demcompare.readthedocs.io/en/stable/userguide/statistics.html\#metrics}{stats metrics}
are organized around
\sphinxhref{https://demcompare.readthedocs.io/en/stable/userguide/statistics.html\#classification-layers}{classification layers and modes}.

\sphinxAtStartPar
Stats are generated from:
\begin{itemize}
\item {} 
\sphinxAtStartPar
\sphinxstylestrong{input\_ref} when one input dem and statistics only

\item {} 
\sphinxAtStartPar
reprojected \sphinxstylestrong{input\_ref \sphinxhyphen{} input\_sec} difference when statistics only

\item {} 
\sphinxAtStartPar
reprojected and coregistered \sphinxstylestrong{input\_ref \sphinxhyphen{} input\_sec} difference with coregistration and statistics

\end{itemize}
